description:
Welcome to this special winter episode! We’re in the Austrian city of Kitzbühel. A legendary alpine town known for its world-class winter sports and its charming, local, festive atmosphere. We’ll show you the thrill of skiing in the snowy mountains, and ways to enjoy the mountain differently.  So wrap up warm and join us for a magical winter experience in the Alps.

This full version is available for a limited time. For our complete library, become a member or download the TriptoVR app on Meta or Pico.

Click the *Join* button now to become a VR Gorilla YouTube member, unlocking access to the full video and our complete collection of full-length videos. https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6AXBF-78lNa3_TjAIWZWmQ/join
